{"tid":780603,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"費明奴同老婆濕吻放閃","createTime":"2018-08-15T09:22:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-15T10:17:59.000Z","uid":54373,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9edfca489f2be76338f40feac026c34c2f4060e3","tid":780603,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T09:22:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images-sports.now.com/sport/news/9/059/17698704059/17700466207_600x342.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-sports.now.com%2Fsport%2Fnews%2F9%2F059%2F17698704059%2F17700466207_600x342.png&h=8e569ba1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=m9ifQ2MdTw74ASouMAz6ojCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=1f1d1ec0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】利物浦中場菲臘比古天奴搞驚喜派對，而巴西同胞羅拔圖法明奴同老婆晒濕吻激情相，搶盡風頭。<br />\n<br />\n利物浦打吡戰輕取愛華頓3:1，24歲的古天奴射入靚波並順水推舟，為老婆Aine舉行驚喜的生日派對，認真夠體貼。<br />\n<br />\n古天奴邀請了紅軍隊友出席，巴西鄉里羅拔圖法明奴（Roberto Firmino）也攜同太太Larissa Pereira華麗現身。<br />\n<br />\n巴西人天性熱情，無拘無束，法明奴同太太在宴會上情到濃時卿卿我我，情不自禁濕吻起來，脷疊脷，送「福利」，實行令網民同樣血脈沸騰。"},{"pid":"65fd2ee60430fcd84a42b3ae4dddc0eb8c523e59","tid":780603,"uid":199296,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T09:24:15.000Z","msg":"想像下佢地影果一秒嘅情況"},{"pid":"8daf6c568b7d5d80ee49df412eb9ec30da2f359c","tid":780603,"uid":54373,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T09:27:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.thesportreview.com/wp-content/uploads/firmino-wife-10-1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thesportreview.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Ffirmino-wife-10-1.jpg&h=ae01944d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DB36CFLXYAAt3-C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDB36CFLXYAAt3-C.jpg&h=827fd7cb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6e9a57861f8abab576c7a703e51a72c6d8092109","tid":780603,"uid":29993,"l